{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/nana-tanpa-suara-komik-tuna-rungu/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Nana Tanpa Suara: Suka-duka Gadis Tuna Rungu di Pedesaan","content":"<p>Seperti apa rasanya hidup di bawah stigma dan pandangan buruk orang lain? Bagaimana rasanya jika tidak ada orang yang memahami diri kamu? Inilah yang dirasakan oleh Nana, gadis tuna rungu yang tinggal di desa bersama ayahnya.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_48805\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48805\" data-attachment-id=\"48805\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/nana-tanpa-suara-komik-tuna-rungu/attachment/01-nana-tanpa-suara/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-nana-tanpa-suara\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-nana-tanpa-suara-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48805\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg\" alt=\"nana tanpa suara\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-nana-tanpa-suara-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48805\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div>\n<p>Nana sudah menjadi tuna rungu sejak lahir, sehingga membuatnya sulit berkomunikasi dengan orang lain. Ditambah, Nana memiliki rambut gimbal alami yang dianggap orang membawa kesialan.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_48806\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48806\" data-attachment-id=\"48806\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/nana-tanpa-suara-komik-tuna-rungu/attachment/02-nana-tanpa-suara/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-nana-tanpa-suara\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-nana-tanpa-suara-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48806\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-nana-tanpa-suara-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48806\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div>\n<p>Meskipun dipandang rendah oleh warga desa dan bahkan keluarganya sendiri, Nana masih menemukan kenyamanan dari sang ayah, serta Danang yang bekerja pada ayahnya. Saat ayah dan Danang pergi kerja, Nana menghabiskan waktu mengurus rumah serta membuat pahatan kayu.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_48807\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48807\" data-attachment-id=\"48807\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/nana-tanpa-suara-komik-tuna-rungu/attachment/03-nana-tanpa-suara/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-nana-tanpa-suara\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-nana-tanpa-suara-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48807\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-nana-tanpa-suara-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48807\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div>\n<p>Kehidupan sehari-hari Nana ini menjadi premis utama dari komik Nana Tanpa Suara. Komik ciptaan Endar Novianto ini tak hanya menjual drama kehidupan gadis dengan disabilitas, namun juga merepresentasikan sosok Nana yang tuna rungu dengan sangat akurat.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_48808\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48808\" data-attachment-id=\"48808\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/nana-tanpa-suara-komik-tuna-rungu/attachment/04-nana-tanpa-suara/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-nana-tanpa-suara\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-nana-tanpa-suara-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48808\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-nana-tanpa-suara-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48808\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div>\n<p>Nana berkomunikasi dengan bahasa isyarat, yang ditampilkan dengan sangat intuitif. Kamu bisa memahami bagaimana Nana menggunakan bahasa isyarat dengan adanya berbagai alat bantu. Gerakan tangan Nana ditampilkan dengan sangat jelas, dan dibantu dengan instruksi panah untuk menggambarkan gerakan tangan Nana. Mungkin sehabis membaca komik ini, kamu juga bisa belajar bahasa isyarat, lho?</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_48809\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48809\" data-attachment-id=\"48809\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/nana-tanpa-suara-komik-tuna-rungu/attachment/05-nana-tanpa-suara/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-nana-tanpa-suara\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-nana-tanpa-suara-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48809\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-nana-tanpa-suara-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48809\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div>\n<p>Tak hanya menampilkan kisah sehari-hari Nana, ternyata komik ini juga menyajikan sebuah kisah petualangan menarik! Meski tuna rungu, Nana ternyata punya kemampuan untuk berbicara dengan benda-benda!</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_48810\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48810\" data-attachment-id=\"48810\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/nana-tanpa-suara-komik-tuna-rungu/attachment/06-nana-tanpa-suara/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/06-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-nana-tanpa-suara\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/06-nana-tanpa-suara-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/06-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48810\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/06-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/06-nana-tanpa-suara.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/06-nana-tanpa-suara-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48810\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div>\n<p>Di tengah-tengah kehidupan Nana dan kemampuannya berbicara dengan benda, ada satu sosok yang selalu terbayang di kepala Nana. Ia selalu memimpikan sesosok patung kijang bertubuh manusia, yang konon katanya dilihat pula oleh almarhum ibunya. Apa maksud dari sosok kijang itu?</p>\n<p>Nantikan kelanjutan komik Nana Tanpa Suara, setiap hari Selasa pukul 19:00 WIB <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/nana-tanpa-suara\">hanya di CIAYO Comics!</a> Jangan lupa juga untuk <em>subscribe</em> biar kamu nggak ketinggalan <em>update</em> episode terbarunya! Kamu punya komik <em>fantasy </em>atau komik <em>slice of life </em>sendiri dan ingin kamu terbitkan? Ikuti <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ciayo-comics-challenge-vol-3-total-hadiahnya-450-juta-rupiah/\">CIAYO Comics Challenge Vol. 3</a> dengan total hadiah 450 juta Rupiah!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"00af87ee-ca4c-5f7f-9ced-a8bc04a6c396"}}}